==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Contrastimulant
<hw>Con`tra*stim"u*lant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Counteracting the effects of stimulants; relating to a course of
medical treatment based on a theory of contrastimulants.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>An agent which counteracts
the effect of a stimulant.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Contrate</ent>⟦br⟧
